{Speech 2}{}{Hi there! A new person, at least! Maybe buy me a drink?}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{I'm @pname@. Why not, let's down some shots. [You spend 2 coins]}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Ehm, later maybe.@@Sorry, i'm not in the talking mood right now.}
{Speech 3}{}{Very nice. You are @sex@|good boy|good girl|!}
{Speech 3 Answer 4}{}{You bet. Another one? [Yoy spend 2 coins] Tell me what's happening around the town?}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Excuse me, I have to go!}
{Speech 4}{}{Our town almost hasn't changed in the past few years. And since Metzger and his dogs are gone, no one's afraid of enslavement anymore. Still, we've got problems with drunks and junkies - the number of sugarmen and bootleggers rocketed, so the problem's just getting worse. And if that wasn't enough, a bunch of shady characters showed up lately. You can't pass the street unnoticed, and if you aren't careful, chances are you will be mugged soon. So keep your eyes open!}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks for the information!}
{Speech 5}{}{Oh, it's you, @pname@! Glad to see you!}
{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{Hi! What's up?}
{Speech 5 Answer 3}{}{Maybe we will drink in the name of our friendship? [You spend 2 coins]}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{I'll be back later.@@Hello, sorry, but i need to go!@@Oh, it's you? Where i can find the bathroom?}
{Speech 6}{}{Nothing new here, let's drink?@@I'm sitting here for a long time, nothing's changed.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Alrighty then, i'll be back soon.}
{Speech 7}{}{You see a women in the bar. She smiling at you] Oh, a fresh face! Maybe you treat me a drink or two?}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{Yehhh, drinks! [She takes 2 coins from your pocket]}
{Speech 7 Answer 9}{}{Mmmm...@@Auhhhh!@@Huuuuuh!@@Emmmm!}
{Speech 8}{}{You are @sex@|nice boy|nice girl|! Alright, go for a walk.}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{Ok-eh.}
{Speech 9}{}{You don't look ok.}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{Not!}
